title: Beirut
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Lebanese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Restaurant with indoor dining room and patio serves several large-portioned vegan salads and appetizers, such as hummus, babaganoush, eggplant moussaka, fattoush, tabouli, other green salads, lentil soup, in-house-made pita bread and pizza. Drinks include tea, beer and wine.
